Teach WASI libc about host filesystem mode bits and chmod.

WASI preview1 filestat exposes file type but not POSIX permission bits. Agent OS
provides those bits through the shared host_fs import so native C tools can use
ordinary stat/access/chmod semantics without per-program patches.

